{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"TextTrack.language","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/language","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVTT_API\">WebVTT API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack\"><code>TextTrack</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/activeCues\"><code>activeCues</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/cues\"><code>cues</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/inBandMetadataTrackDispatchType\"><code>inBandMetadataTrackDispatchType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/kind\"><code>kind</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/label\"><code>label</code></a></li><li><em><code>language</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/mode\"><code>mode</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/addCue\"><code>addCue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/removeCue\"><code>removeCue()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/cuechange_event\"><code>cuechange</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebVTT</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrackCue\"><code>TextTrackCue</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrackCueList\"><code>TextTrackCueList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrackList\"><code>TextTrackList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TrackEvent\"><code>TrackEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VTTCue\"><code>VTTCue</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VTTRegion\"><code>VTTRegion</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>language</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack\"><code>TextTrack</code></a> interface returns the language of the text track.</p>\n<p>This uses the same values as the HTML <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-lang\"><code>lang</code></a> attribute. These values are documented in <a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc5646\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 5646: Tags for Identifying Languages (also known as BCP 47)</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A string containing a language identifier. For example, <code>\"en-US\"</code> for United States English or <code>\"pt-BR\"</code> for Brazilian Portuguese.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In the following example the value of <code>language</code> is printed to the console.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> video <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'video'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> track <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> video<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addTextTrack</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"captions\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Captions\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"en-US\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntrack<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"showing\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>track<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>language<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[],"query":"api.TextTrack.language"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.TextTrack.language","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/language/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The language read-only property of the TextTrack interface returns the language of the text track.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:19:45.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/texttrack/language","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/texttrack/language/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f7dae62645a2c735ed6f6ed63f664bf279fdfc4b","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack","title":"TextTrack"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextTrack/language","title":"TextTrack.language"}],"pageTitle":"TextTrack.language - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}